data.description: Take advantage of the PRICE DROP on this beautiful move-in-ready home! Seller's relocating hate to leave this 1.5 story in the perfect cul de sac! Come checkout this sprawling 5 bedroom, 4 full bath home with room for all. You will notice the new oak wood floors and appealing natural light when you open the front door. This spacious home has been well-kept and has beautiful new renovations throughout. Fresh carpet and interior paint. Updated and modern kitchen that flows beautifully into the living room complete with new fireplace facing. Primary bedroom offers lots of space with a freshly updated bathroom and huge walk-in. Large bedroom sizes to accommodate any age. Main level laundry. Extremely close to shopping, dining and Liberty School District schools for all ages.
